{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_51_02",
  "title": "川咲さくら 2話 魚魚っとバイク",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "お邪魔しま～す\nさくらちゃんのおうちに来るの、久しぶりね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me~.\nIt’s been a while since I last visited your house‚ Sakura-chan~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0999999125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.1892967622
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "どうぞどうぞ。お父さんもお母さんも出掛けてるし\n好きなようにくつろいじゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come in‚ come in. My mom and dad are out‚\nso make yourself at home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8226300955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.1892967622
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ遠慮なく\nあそこの棚にある、美味しそうなお菓子を～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ I’ll gladly take\nthose delicious-looking snacks on the shelf without hesitation~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4666662613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.4194100221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4194100221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.4860755444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "なーんてね、冗談よ。ふふ、それじゃあ早速\nさくらちゃんのお誕生日企画の準備をしましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just kidding‚ it was a joke. Fufu‚ well then‚ shall we\nstart preparing for Sakura-chan’s birthday project?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4333315292,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12100.0018041,
          "startTime": 41.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.9666875761
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　昔の写真から、雑誌に載せても良さそうなのを\n選ぶんだったよね。アルバムは、確かあの辺に～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! We’re choosing which old photos are okay to publish\nin the magazine‚ right? The photo albums should be around there~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6000209094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.6000209094
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん、ありがとうございます\n企画のアイデアまで出してくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Haruko-san.\nYou even came up with ideas for the project.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5000209094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.9666873218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "いいのよ、私にも手伝わせて？　いえ、手伝わせなさい\n勝手にお菓子を食べちゃった罰なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s fine. Let me help you. No‚ you must let me help.\nAs punishment for eating my sweets without permission.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4333312749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.6984561604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、バラエティには慣れてるの。こういう家族が\n出演する企画なら、昔話や写真の紹介が鉄板だと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I’m used to variety shows. For a project that involves family‚\ntalking about the past and showing photos are a surefire way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5666646082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。ファンの人達も、さくらの昔の話は\n気になるはずですし。きっと、盛り上がります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. The fans would be curious to hear about Sakura’s past‚\nso it would be really exciting for them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4738461894,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3733.3333410999926,
          "startTime": 78.2071795305
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.9738461972
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、遙子ちゃん、アルバム持ってきたよ～！\nあと、私なりに写真を選んでみました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ Haruko-chan‚ I brought the photo albums~!\nAlso‚ I’ve chosen some photos myself!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4738446634,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4259.487398399998,
          "startTime": 88.7333320618
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.5738446634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ、ちっちゃい頃のさくら、可愛い\nけど……なんで半目の写真ばっかり選んだの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ Sakura was so cute when she was little.\nBut… why did you only choose pictures where your eyes are half-closed…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1738446634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.7071835917
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "「半目の方が、自然でさくららしいよ」って、前に\nkanaさんが言ってくれたことがあって。どうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Your half-closed eyes look more natural and Sakura-like‚”\nkana-san told me that before. How does it look?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1738502583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.540516925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう、ね。半目でも、さくらは可愛いけど……\n私と遙子さんの方でも、選んでみる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-right. You’re cute even with your eyes half-closed‚ but…\nHaruko-san and I will choose some too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4738502583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.4738502583
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.040516925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、選んでくれてありがとう\nどれも思い出が一杯あるから、迷っちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ thanks for choosing.\nEvery photo is filled with memories‚ so it’s hard to choose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2071825744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.6738492411
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、私達も、さくらちゃんの昔話が一杯聞けて\n嬉しかった。でも……本当に苦労してきたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ we enjoyed hearing all your old stories‚ Sakura-chan.\nBut… you’ve really been through a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.3666579961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.693350204
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、そんなことないよ。なんでみんなと\n違うんだろうって、思うことはあったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it’s not like that. I wondered\nwhy I was different from everyone else…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.093350204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.0600148362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "今はこうして元気に、みんなと過ごせてるから\n苦労したのは、きっと、お父さんとお母さんの方だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now I’m healthy and I can spend time with everyone.\nSo it was probably my parents who had the hardest time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.9600148362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.8933344366
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "だから、撮影当日は、心を込めて歌おうと思うんだ\nお父さんとお母さんに、伝わるように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I’m going to sing with all my heart on the day of the shoot.\nSo that my feelings reach my mom and dad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.5600011033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.5266677699
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんの歌なら、きっと伝わるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it’s your song‚ your feelings will surely reach them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.5266677699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.0964204551
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
